# No comments

Never write comments in source or config that CI would treat as code:

- No `//`, `/* */`, `///`, or `//!` in `.rs`, `.ts`, `.tsx`, `.js`, `.jsx`
- No `--` SQL comments or `/* */` in `.sql`
- No `/* */` in `.css`

If something needs explaining, use clear names and/or a `docs/**/*.md` file.

Do not add comment-only commits or "explain in comments" refactors. Prefer renaming and markdown docs.
